726426f-a.title: Queens: Court Square - Jackson Avenue
726426f-a.text:
Court Square (left, not seen), north from the Pennsylvania Railroad yards to Jackson Ave., showing in the foreground the jail. Beyond it is the Court house of Queens County. At the right is shown the Metropolitan Life Insurance Company printing plant.

About 1927.
